  <img src="https://images.thrillophilia.com/image/upload/s--Xxvuj_fZ--/c_fill,dpr_1.0,f_auto,fl_strip_profile,g_center,h_450,q_auto,w_753/v1/images/photos/000/042/689/original/1521531866_resorts_in_mumbai.jpg.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="..." style="height: 200px; width: 250px;">
  <div class="card-body">
    
  <h5 class="card-title">The Machan Resort, Avtan(97 km from mumbai)</h5>
    <p class="card-text" >30 to 45 feet above the forest. This Mumbai resorts within 100Km feature innovative accommodation options and offer a number of facilities and activities to keep its guests engaged and entertained. Considered as one of the best resorts near Mumbai, it is surrounded by lush greenery and overlooks the canopied beauty of Jambulne, which is a mere 2.5 hours drive from Mumbai. A green island in itself, the resort is 100 percent off the grid and run only on sustainable resources. Each machan has been carefully designed to minimize the impact on the environment.<br>

In here are three different types of machans – the Heritage Machan, the Canopy Machan and the Forest Machan. The Heritage Machan is built around a wild fig tree and is hosted at a height of 45 feet above the forest floor. This delightful stay hangs over the edge of a precipice and is very popular for its unique architectural design, elegant interiors and breathtaking views of the valley below it. The Machan has been designed as a family unit with an open plan.</p>
  </div>
</div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-4">
    <div class="card" style="width: 15.8rem;">
  <img src="https://images.thrillophilia.com/image/upload/s--u0PCH3tC--/c_fill,dpr_1.0,f_auto,fl_strip_profile,g_center,h_450,q_auto,w_753/v1/images/photos/000/147/757/original/1552282444_fariyas-resort-lonavla-exte.jpg.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="..." style="height: 200px; width: 250px;">
  <div class="card-body">
    
  <h5 class="card-title">Fariyaz Resort, Lonavla(84 km from mumbai)</h5>
    <p class="card-text" >The Fariyas Resort is a five-star resort and offers the best of comfort, accommodation, services and amenities. In here are deluxe rooms, premium rooms and suites for its guests. The aesthetic deluxe rooms are perfect for relaxation. Each one comes with a double bed, a sofa cum bed. The furnishings of the resort enhance the beauty of the rooms and impart cosiness and warmth. Every room comes with a private balcony which presents a breathtaking view of the Frichley Hills that surround the property and it is one of the best resort near Mumbai for 1-night stay.<br>

The good resorts near Mumbai are elegantly designed in a contemporary style to suit the modern requirements of guests. Each room has contemporary interiors, a range of modern facilities and comes with private balconies. All the accommodations are centrally air-conditioned, have well-appointed features such as auto wake up call, direct dialling facility, WiFi, electronic safe, multi-channel television, mini bar, king-sized beds and more.</p>

  </div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-sm-4">
    <div class="card" style="width: 15.8rem;">
  <img src="https://images.thrillophilia.com/image/upload/s--BaMx8Ono--/c_fill,dpr_1.0,f_auto,fl_strip_profile,g_center,h_450,q_auto,w_753/v1/images/photos/000/040/351/original/1521532616_resorts_in_mumbai.jpg.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="..." style="height: 200px; width: 250px;">
  <div class="card-body">
    
  <h5 class="card-title">The Dukes Retreat, Khandala (78 km from Mumbai)</h5>
    <p class="card-text" >The Mystica Resort is situated in the picturesque valley of Lonavala and Khandala and is one of the finest resorts near Mumbai. It overlooks the beautiful ghats of Khandala and provides the perfect getaway for any traveller. Snuggled on the beautiful Sahayadri Mountains, the retreat stands on 5 acres and offers 150 well appointed rooms and suites fitted with all modern amenities.<br>

This Mumbai resort within 100 km is one of the best resorts near Mumbai and ideal for leisure holidays, honeymoons, wedding ceremonies and conferences. The accommodation comprises of doubles, twins, deluxe, interconnecting and a selection of suites including Junior, Penthouse and Presidential. All rooms have been infused with contemporary elegance and international designs. Most rooms offer a fabulous view of the beautiful valley and hill. Avail of facilities such as a lagoon swimming pool with waterfall, 15000 square feet lawn for marriage ceremonies and private parties, boating in private lake, bar at the house boat, indoor games and children’s playground.</p>

